  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action adventure game. Play as Inna, Daughter of the Void and discover this magic world. Try many different magic spells and face unique enemies on your path. Interesting 2d hand drawn world, and unique style make it worth your time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try different Sword arts & magic spells.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483930/extras/d93834245a6a9623c5d369bdd1941b73.poster.avif?t=1739726631\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483930/extras/d93834245a6a9623c5d369bdd1941b73.webm?t=1739726631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483930/extras/d93834245a6a9623c5d369bdd1941b73.mp4?t=1739726631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manga like, Inna's Hidden past</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483930/extras/810fb6618857ec6bb96cb4aea8c9fb83.avif?t=1739726631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483930/extras_big/810fb6618857ec6bb96cb4aea8c9fb83.avif?t=1739726631 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Colorful characters and their stories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483930/extras/565427967fe7dcc4d90666d03701a29a.avif?t=1739726631\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/24839